data.description: Welcome home! This like new home, built in 2017, is on a beautiful and quiet street. This is the One you've been looking for! This gorgeous Ranch style home has 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with over 1600 square feet and an open floor plan, you will have plenty of room for the whole family! Features include; an open concept kitchen and dining room, split bedroom floor plan, a spacious fenced in backyard, and an upgraded water filtration system including emergency water tank installed. This home is in the "A" rated Grovetown School District,  just minutes from shopping and dining, and less than 15 minutes from Gate 6 on Fort Eisenhower (formerly Fort Gordon).
